				Identify the odd one from these tags: &lt;span&gt;, &lt;p&gt;, &lt;a&gt;, &lt;i&gt;  and state the reason?							
			</p>
			<p>
				<strong>Ans:</strong>
				&lt;p&gt; because it's a block-level element and the other tags are inline elements.
