			<p>
				<strong>Ans:</strong>
				A mockup of the element being centered by this CSS block is hidden in the comments. <br>
				&lt;style&gt;
				div.css-block
					display: block {
					background-color: green;
					margin: 0;
					position: absolute;
					width: 200px;
  					height: 200px;
  					top: 50%;
  					left: 50%;
  					margin-right: -50%;
  					transform: translate(-50% -50%)
  					}
  				&lt;/style&gt;

  				<!-- my comment has the element my CSS is styling here: 
