				<strong>Qus: 19</strong>
				Give an example of input field that takes phone number with format "123-456-7890"? 			
			</p>
			<p>
				<strong>Ans:</strong>
					function phonenumber(inputtxt)
					{
  						var phoneno = /^\(?([0-9]{3})\)?[-]?([0-9]{3})[-]?([0-9]{4})$/;
  						if((inputtxt.value.match(phoneno))
    			    {
   				   return true;
   				     }
   				   else
   				     {
    			    alert("message");
    			    return false;
    			    }
				}
